window.VBPAppPageSettings={showPageSettings:!1,pageSettingsTab:"general",pageSettings:{seoTitle:"",seoDescription:"",ogImage:"",ogTitle:"",ogDescription:"",customCss:"",customJs:"",pageClass:"",pageId:""},openPageSettings:function(){this.showPageSettings=!0},savePageSettings:function(){var e=Alpine.store("vbp").settings;e.pageSettings=this.pageSettings,Alpine.store("vbp").settings=e,Alpine.store("vbp").isDirty=!0,this.showPageSettings=!1,this.showNotification("Configuración de página guardada","success")},selectOgImage:function(){var e=this;if("undefined"!=typeof wp&&wp.media){var t=wp.media({title:"Seleccionar imagen para redes sociales",button:{text:"Usar esta imagen"},multiple:!1,library:{type:"image"}});t.on("select",(function(){var i=t.state().get("selection").first().toJSON();e.pageSettings.ogImage=i.url})),t.open()}}};